issueSharesForAmount.t.sol
└── when amount is zero
    ├── it should mint zero receipt tokens
    └── when amount is greater than zero
        ├── when the recipient is the zero address
        │   └── it should revert with ERC20InvalidReceiver error
        └── when the recipient is not the zero address
            ├── when the totalSupply is zero
            │   └── it should mint the same shares as amount
            └── when the totalSupply is greater than zero
                └── it should mint shares for the amount multiplied by totalSupply and divided by freeFunds